    ColumnLayer Example¶

    This is a quick example notebook to show how to use the ColumnLayer.

    This is derived from @cboettig's example in this issue.

    Dependencies¶

    Install uv and then launch this notebook with:

    uvx juv run examples/column-layer.ipynb

    (The uvx command is included when installing uv).
